insert into historial_expedientes(expediente_id,fecha_suceso,descripcion,is_deleted) values((select ei.id from expedientes_intranet ei inner join expediente_datos_personales edp on edp.id=ei.expediente_datos_personales_id where edp.nombre='FLORENCIA'and edp.apellido1='DAVILA'and apellido2='GARCIA'),'2021-05-13','Ana: Llamad de May, Jefa Secc. Mayores (659 790 422). Ya tienen informe del hospital, le van a dar el alta. Diagnósitico: "Demencia en estudio" y "Trastorno bipolar actualmente estabilizado". **Le dan plaza en la Residencia de Mayores de Santiago de Alcántara. ······························································································································································································· Llamo a Pedro, Técnico de SS.TT.-CC (927 00 42 39): hoy le hacen la PCR en el hptal. si da negativo mañana mismo podrá ingresar. En la residencia ya lo saben. Me facilita el teléfono de la Directora. ·························································································································································································· Llamo a Begoña, directora de la Res. Santiago de Alcántara (680 799 543): ya está al tanto. Le indico que aún no tenemos información acerca de su pensión. Se abonará más adelante cuando tengamos más datos y acceso a sus cuentas. En cuanto a ropa, dicen que tienen en la residencia para estos casos. *Me enviarán la documentación oportuna. ··························································································································································································· Llamo a Celia, TS del HVP-Plas. (78206): el traslado se realizará en ambulancia mañana. *Ya ha pedido la PCR a la Psiquiatra, Carmen Pérez, y le cofirmará, que si la PCR es negativa se le trasladará a la residencia. ····························································································································································································· Envío correo a Toni-Futuex y a Raquel, TS SSASB, comunicándolo.','2');
